title: Speaker Mike Johnson says he thinks standalone Israel aid bill will pass the House this week
description: The White House had asked Congress to pass a broader national security package that also included aid to Ukraine amid its ongoing war with Russia.

title: Iran and its proxy forces loom over Israel-Hamas war, sparking fears of wider regional conflict
description: Israel's bombardment of Hamas in Gaza could spread into a wider Middle East war involving Iran and its proxies in Lebanon, Syria and Iraq, experts say.
